<div class="container">
    <div class="is-flex is-justify-content-space-evenly">
        <button class="button" id="lore-rhefir">Rhefir</button>
        <button class="button" id="lore-nehneh">Neh</button>
        <a class="button" target="_blank" href="https://minipi.zirk.eu/">Minipi</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        Welcome in my amazing lore tab, where I do my little creative things, sometimes with the help of friends<br/>
        "So what are you going to do with that", you might ask<br/>
        Well, nothing! But it sure is fun to create
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="container" id="answer-lore-rhefir">
        <h2 class="subtitle">Basic concepts</h2>
        <p>
            {{ lore.basics.description | join("<br/>") | raw }}
        </p>
        <div class="is-flex is-flex-wrap-wrap" id="lore-basics-flex">
            {% for e in lore.basics.data %}
            <div class="card lore-card-basics">
                <header class="card-header">
                    <p class="card-header-title">{{ e.name }}</p>
                </header>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="content">
                    {{ e.description | join("<br/>") | raw }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <h2 class="subtitle">Advanced concepts</h2>
        <p>
            {{ lore.world.description | join("<br/>") | raw }}
        </p>
        <div class="lore-display">
            <div class="lore-display-btns">
                {% for e in lore.world.data %}
                    <div class="{% if e.important %}is-flex{% else %}is-hidden{% endif %} btn-lore-container">
                        <span class="button" disabled>
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                                {{ e.icon }}
                            </span>
                        </span>
                        <button class="btn-lore button" data-summary="{{ e.summary }}" data-description="{{ e.description | join("\n") }}">{{ e.name }}</button>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
                <button class="button" id="lore-see-all">See all</button>
            </div>
            <div id="lore-world-text-container" class="has-text-right">
                <textarea class="textarea" id="lore-world-text" rows="20" readonly>
                </textarea>
                <span id="lore-world-text-button">
                    <label class="label">See more details</label>
                    <label class="switch is-rounded">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="lore-world-text-button-input" />
                        <span class="check"></span>
                    </label>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="subtitle">Timeline</h2>
        <p>
            {{ lore.timeline.json.description | join("<br/>") | raw }}
        </p>
        <div id="lore-timeline">
        </div>
        <script type="application/json" id="lore-timeline-json">
            {{ lore.timeline | replace({'<': '&lt;' }) | raw }}
        </script>
        <h2 class="subtitle">Species</h2>
        <p>
            {{ lore.species.json.description | join("<br/>") | raw }}
        </p>
        <div class="lore-display" id="lore-species">
            <div id="lore-species-network"></div>
            <textarea class="textarea" id="lore-species-text" rows="20" readonly>
            </textarea>
        </div>
        <script type="application/json" id="lore-species-json">
            {{ lore.species.raw | replace({'<': '&lt;' }) | raw }}
        </script>
    </div>
